trans-unit.source: Represents a single property in an [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en enkelt egenskap i en [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"></xref> class with the specified name and value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"> </xref> klassen med det angitte navnet og verdien.

trans-unit.source: The property name.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsnavnet.

trans-unit.source: The property value.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien.

trans-unit.source: Creates a deep or shallow copy of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en dype eller lite kopi av det <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A shallow copy of a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> references the same XML element as the original.
trans-unit.target: En lite kopi av en <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>refererer til samme XML-elementet som opprinnelig.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>

trans-unit.source: Modifications to the name or value of a shallow copy will be reflected in both copies.
trans-unit.target: Endringer i navnet eller verdien av et lite eksemplar gjenspeiles i begge kopier.

trans-unit.source: However, depending on property evaluation, the two copies could have different <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid avhengig egenskap evalueringen to kopier kan ha forskjellige <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A>egenskapsverdier.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty.FinalValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: A deep copy of a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> creates a new XML element to reference so that both copies of the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> can be independently modified.
trans-unit.target: En dyp kopi av en <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>oppretter en ny XML-elementet å referere til slik at både overfører av den <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>kan endres uavhengig.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>opprette dype kopi av det <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildProperty"> </xref>; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
